I love it, and my highest character was 29 when I got there (32 now).<br>
The only GM event I've been to was a raid on Paw, but I had a blast.  The GM seemed to be kinda lost (At one point he got us all locked in the jail, and had to pop through the door to get us out, that had me laughing pretty hard) but other than that, it was nice.  I died a bunch, but the GM rez'd us all (Not CS Rez, but the Cleric Epic one...Reviv whatever) repeatedly :P<br>
As for the lack of low levels...You just have to know where to look.  I personally love it, low competition, and the best part is, everyone there knows what they're doing, no real idiots so far (OK, maybe one, but he wasn't malicious really).<br>
And as for the economy, I love that too.<br>
Between GM Events, luck, vendors, and auctioning, I've managed to upgrade my weapons from Burning Rapier and Servant's Blade (I'm not twinked) to a Gold Plated Koshignata and a Centi Shortsword (I found it at a vendor for 7 plat, you can't beat that) and also picked up an Iksar regen BP :P<br>
The only downside is I don't really have any friends there, but I didn't have any left on Fennin either, and there are people I've actually grouped with pretty regularly, which is nice.<br>
<br>
And as a rogue, while I do have some trouble solo'ing, since there's almost no competition for hunting areas, I can pretty much pick what mobs I want to hunt if I am solo'ing :P <p>"Age and wisdom don't always go together, I've found. ... Some people just become stupid with more authority." -- Terry Pratchett</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umardocthedwarf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mardoc the Dwarf</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/28/02 8:14:31 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23071.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Legends Server - Question</span><hr size=1> i'm tempted to move over, i'll be charged more but it sounds like lots of fun<br>
